===私家车===
从墨尔本市西北开上M1[[高速公路|高速道]]，一般二十分钟可到达。但周日请注意[[交通堵塞|交通堵塞]]情况。

从智朗市北面开上M1[[高速公路|高速道]]，一般十五分钟可到达。

机场内[[停车场|停车场]]第一天收费15[[澳元|澳元]]，以后每天收费6[[澳元|澳元]]，不需要预约。

===火车===
距离机场最近的[[火车站|火车站]]为'''Lara'''站，要估算好时间，下车后骑[[自行车|自行车]]10[[分钟|分钟]]即可到达，或搭乘[[计程车|计程车]]。

===直升飞机===

==其他信息==

[[File:C-17_Globemaster_III_at_Avalon_2005_1.jpg|thumb]]）<!-- at Avalon Airport, Australia, March 2005-->]]

每两年一度的[[澳大利亚国际航空展览|澳大利亚国际航空展览]]在此机场举行，请参照航空展的公式网址以确认展出时间。<!--Avalon Airport hosts the [[Australian_International_Airshow|Australian International Airshow]], which is held every two years. It is also the site of one of Qantas' heavy maintenance and engineering facilities.<ref>{{cite news |title=Threat to Qantas Melbourne jobs |author=Stephen Moynihan |date=March 10, 2006 |url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/threat-to-qantas-melbourne-jobs/2006/03/09/1141701635131.html |publisher=[[The_Age|The Age]] |accessdate=2007-03-03}}</ref>

Avalon Airport was one of three sites being considered as the new site for the [[Melbourne_Markets|Wholesale Fruit and Vegetable Markets]] which are to be moved from [[West_Melbourne|West Melbourne]] to allow development of the [[Port_of_Melbourne|Port of Melbourne]].{{Fact|time=2007-11-01T17:03:33Z|date=March 2007}} A site in [[Epping,_Victoria|Epping]] was ultimately chosen as the preferred site.

The land on which Avalon Airport lies is part of the Lara Lea escarpment which is bounded by the [[You_Yangs|You Yangs]], [[Corio_Bay|Corio Bay]] and [[Melbourne_Water|Melbourne Water]] sewage treatment agistment paddocks. The airport continues to fall under the jurisdiction of the [[Australian_Department_of_Defence|Australian Department of Defence]].

A Qantas 747-338 ('''Nalanji Dreaming'''), which is painted in a colourful aboriginal livery, is currently in long term open-air storage at Avalon Airport
-->

